data.description: MOSS LAKE WATERFRONT HOME in Cross Creek Subdivision! WELCOME HOME to this uniquely designed property with lots of curb appeal sitting on a .78 acre residential lot. This home consists of 4 Bedrooms and 4 Full Baths with 2 additional bonus rooms upstairs. Two-story living room including a beautiful stone fireplace with gas logs. Off of the living room you will find a sunroom where you can enjoy year-round views of the lake & pool. Newer decks, perfect for outdoor entertainment, overlooking the backyard and the 20x40 in-ground swimming pool. Pool pump replaced in 2019 along with new black fencing surrounding the pool. Siding replaced in 2021 and new Gas Pack replaced in 2021. Refrigerator will remain. Ample amount of storage throughout the home. Enjoy all of your lake activities at the two story dock with sundeck on top!
